A catastrophe killed billions of people due to monsters suddenly appearing around the world. Some of the survivors became ‘metahumans’, able to fight against the monsters. This causes a huge divide to form between metahumans and regular humans.
Kim Seon-U is a regular human guide for the metahumans’ beast subjugation. On the verge of death, he hears a voice in his head say: “Kill them. Kill them and take their power!”
(Source: KakaoPage, translated and edited)

[Will you join the game?] Giyoung's suddenly thrown into a game of life and death. Not only that but he's also the player with the lowest stats. Still, he's got one skill on his side: the ability to read other players' status! He finds the opportunity of his life when he discovers that Hyunsung is a returner to this world. Now all Giyoung has to do is stick next to Hyunsung and game his way out of this tutorial.
(Source: Tapas)
